@startuml Register_Login_Sequence
autonumber
actor User as "Mobile Client"
boundary AuthController as "Auth Controller"
control UserService as "User Service"
control JwtProvider as "JWT Token Provider"
database MySQL as "MySQL DB"

== Luồng Đăng Ký Tài Khoản ==
User -> AuthController: POST /api/auth/register (email, password, fullName)
activate AuthController
AuthController -> UserService: register(userDto)
activate UserService
UserService -> MySQL: Kiểm tra email tồn tại?
MySQL --> UserService: Kết quả (Chưa tồn tại)
UserService -> UserService: Mã hóa password (BCrypt)
UserService -> MySQL: Save New User Entity
MySQL --> UserService: Thành công
UserService --> AuthController: Trả về User đối tượng
deactivate UserService
AuthController --> User: HTTP 201 Created
deactivate AuthController

== Luồng Đăng Nhập Hệ Thống ==
User -> AuthController: POST /api/auth/login (email, password)
activate AuthController
AuthController -> UserService: login(loginDto)
activate UserService
UserService -> MySQL: Tìm User theo email
MySQL --> UserService: User Entity
UserService -> UserService: Khớp mật khẩu (BCrypt Match)
alt Đăng nhập thành công
    UserService -> JwtProvider: generateToken(User)
    activate JwtProvider
    JwtProvider --> UserService: String AccessToken (JWT)
    deactivate JwtProvider
    UserService --> AuthController: Trả về JwtResponse
    AuthController --> User: HTTP 200 OK + Bearer Token
else Sai thông tin đăng nhập
    UserService --> AuthController: Throw BadCredentialsException
    AuthController --> User: HTTP 401 Unauthorized
end
deactivate UserService
deactivate AuthController
@enduml